			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong>地址：</strong>广州番禺南沙区万顷沙镇新垦15涌</p>
<p>广州番禺百万葵园的介绍词：</p>
<blockquote><p>“十万洛阳牡丹、向日葵一望无际的壮观、樱花飘零、七彩花田的灿漫、玫瑰香远溢清、番禺百万葵园让我们置身于花的海洋！”</p></blockquote>
<p>然而实际情况并非如此！希望广大良善群众不要再像博主一样上当受骗！！白白浪费60+人民币（有再升价的可能性）！<br />
<span id="more-47506"></span><br />
话说博主一直闻其名而未曾有幸前往，前不久看及新浪微博上有人转发这样一条微博：</p>
<blockquote><p>广州南沙百万葵园暑假到8月25号期间学生票（<strong>在校大中小学生</strong>）凭学生证 <strong>￥20</strong> 原价 ￥65 广州地铁四号线3蕉门站落转百万葵园专线车 爱旅游爱摄影嘀大家千万不要错过啦~</p></blockquote>
<p>于是特意赶在那之前去。</p>
<p>失望！！非常失望！！！</p>
<p>首先……我的证买不到学生票啦，借朋友的学生证也不行，售票的说相片不像。啧！原价就原价咯，园内漂亮值得的话也ok啦～实际非也！！！</p>
<p>然后……里面那一点残花败柳，啧啧，我只能猜测是我去的时候不对，看不到漂亮的葵花啦。<div id="attachment_47509" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 710px"><a href="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040175.jpg" onclick="return hs.expand(this);" class="highslide-image"><img src="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040175-700x525.jpg" alt="image" title="Click to enlarge" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">耷拉着脑袋的向日葵君，乃肿么了</p></div><br />
<div id="attachment_47519" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 710px"><a href="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040174.jpg" onclick="return hs.expand(this);" class="highslide-image"><img src="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040174-700x525.jpg" alt="image" title="Click to enlarge" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">所谓的七彩花田，啧，跟宣传相差好远</p></div></p>
<p>名字叫百万葵园，我顾名思义，里面没有九百万株向日葵也有接近一百万株的向日葵吧，至少在视觉上有种向日葵花海的感觉吧！非也！！！<br />
<div id="attachment_47508" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 710px"><a href="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-9.jpg" onclick="return hs.expand(this);" class="highslide-image"><img src="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-9-700x525.jpg" alt="image" title="Click to enlarge" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">小小的向日葵田</p></div></p>
<p>好吧…… ╮(╯-╰)╭，即便如此，这里仍然有许多影楼过来拍婚纱相。<br />
<div id="attachment_47510" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 710px"><a href="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040162.jpg" onclick="return hs.expand(this);" class="highslide-image"><img src="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040162-700x525.jpg" alt="image" title="Click to enlarge" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">在这里拍婚纱相是有多“折堕”啊！</p></div></p>
<p>是是是，我必须承认这里有许多供影楼摄影所用的各种造型的小建筑。百万葵园，你不如改名XX主题摄影基地？！<br />
<div id="attachment_47511" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 710px"><a href="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040125.jpg" onclick="return hs.expand(this);" class="highslide-image"><img src="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040125-700x525.jpg" alt="image" title="Click to enlarge" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">灰兔子，好可爱，看，耳朵上还别着一朵小花呢～</p></div><br />
<div id="attachment_47507" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 710px"><a href="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-2.jpg" onclick="return hs.expand(this);" class="highslide-image"><img src="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-2-700x525.jpg" alt="image" title="Click to enlarge" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">园内的仿风车造型建筑</p></div><br />
<div id="attachment_47515" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 710px"><a href="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040146.jpg" onclick="return hs.expand(this);" class="highslide-image"><img src="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040146-700x525.jpg" alt="image" title="Click to enlarge" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">婚纱相取景地之一，花藤缠绕的旧楼梯</p></div><br />
<div id="attachment_47518" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 710px"><a href="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040161.jpg" onclick="return hs.expand(this);" class="highslide-image"><img src="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040161-700x525.jpg" alt="image" title="Click to enlarge" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">婚纱相取景地之二，池上桥</p></div></p>
<p>即便有以上各式建筑物，但也不能掩饰这里其实就是个乡下地方！你不用花钱，在任何你所在城市郊区旁边的农田都能看到如此景象！<br />
<div id="attachment_47513" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 710px"><a href="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040144.jpg" onclick="return hs.expand(this);" class="highslide-image"><img src="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040144-700x933.jpg" alt="image" title="Click to enlarge" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">连瓜藤都有，啧，如此田园景象哪里没有，非要花上几十大洋千里迢迢来这里看。</p></div><br />
<div id="attachment_47516" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 710px"><a href="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040149.jpg" onclick="return hs.expand(this);" class="highslide-image"><img src="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040149-700x525.jpg" alt="image" title="Click to enlarge" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">这边厢直接就是菜地了</p></div></p>
<p>当然，盛开的向日葵不是没有，但就那么几株，如何衬得上“百万葵园”的名字？！<br />
<div id="attachment_47512" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 710px"><a href="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040126.jpg" onclick="return hs.expand(this);" class="highslide-image"><img src="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040126-700x525.jpg" alt="image" title="Click to enlarge" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">开得尚算精彩的向日葵</p></div><br />
<div id="attachment_47517" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 710px"><a href="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040158.jpg" onclick="return hs.expand(this);" class="highslide-image"><img src="http://sizheng.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yuki-1040158-700x933.jpg" alt="image" title="Click to enlarge" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">这一小块向日葵田是开得最好的了</p></div></p>
<p>总之呢，我是万分心疼我那65元大洋TAT<br />
博主用亲身经历验证告诉大家，千万别去百万葵园，别再上当受骗了！！！！！</p>
<p>当然，你也可以参考jzhone的这篇博文《<a href="http://www.jzh.me/archives/180.html">猪の生日游记（第2话）——百万葵园篇</a>》，他把失望归咎于天气不好，我也只能怪自己选择错了花期。但其实嘛……这里就是一个坑爹的地方！！！！大家不要浪费钱去了！！！！！</p>
<hr /><small>Copyright &copy; 2005-2011 <a href="http://sizheng.org/">All D's Life</a>. <br /><img src="http://s34.sitemeter.com/meter.asp?site=s34despair" alt="Site Meter" border="0"/><br /> </small>]]></content:encoded>
