<p>富贵路的尽头便是静妙堂。<br />
<a href="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5109/5630438890_964821317d_b.jpg" onclick="return hs.expand(this, {captionId:'caption_1303207854558'});" class="highslide-image"><img src="http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5109/5630438890_964821317d_z.jpg" alt="image" title="Click to enlarge" /></a>
